    <a href="/hot-dog/healthy/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">healthier choices</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can vegans eat Costco hot dogs?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">No, Costco food court hot dogs contain beef and are not vegan. However, Costco sells plant-based sausages from brands like Beyond Meat and Field Roast in their refrigerated sections.</p>
      </div>
